name: Battōjutsu 拔刀/居合 update升级版
description:
第三个：swingver

第三次更新了挥刀，全新的训练集，这一个系列的都放在一起了，方便查找。

挥刀lora推荐chilloutmix、anythingv4.5、PileDream、dlfmaanjffhgkwlMix。权重0.6-0.9。

准备后面再做个纳刀刀的lora，装逼要完成全套。

The third update of swing, a brand new training set, this one series are put together, easy to find.

This lora recommended chilloutmix, anythingv4.5, PileDream, dlfmaanjffhgkwlMix. Weights0.6-0.9.

Plan to do a Retracting the knife lora later, pretend to complete a full set.

/////

fightver：

该版训练集本使用了80%新的图片，使居合的姿势更加具有动感，一定意义上可以算是另一个lora了。需要站着的pose建议使用V1，喜欢战斗姿态则选择新版本。新版本对真人的适用性有所降低，推荐二次元模型。

This version of the training set uses 80% new images, making the pose more dynamic, and in a certain sense, it can be considered as another LORA. For standing poses, it is recommended to use V1, while the new version is more suitable for fightver. The new version's applicability to real people has decreased, so it is recommended for use with 2D models.

/////

鉴于居合难以使用prompt调用，于是做了一个居合的lora。

trigger words 是battōjutsu, (holding weapen:1.3)，你也可以加上 sheath, unsheathing,

权重0.5-0.9，三次元二次元模型都行。

如果你使用Hires. Fix的话，Denoising需要调低到0.4以下。

 In view of the difficulty of using prompt for battōjutsu, a lora for it was created. The trigger words are battōjutsu , (holding weapen:1.3), and you can also add sheath , unsheathing. Weight can be set between 0.5 and 0.9, and both 3D and 2D models are suitable.

If you are using Hires. Fix, denoising may need to be set below 0.4.
